Library API

Overview
Dockerized REST API built with Node.js and Express featuring JWT authentication, PostgreSQL integration, and Prometheus-based observability with Grafana dashboards.

Tech Stack
- Node.js
- Express
- PostgreSQL
- Docker/Docker Compose
- Prometheus
- Grafana
- JWT Authentication

Architecture
Client → Express API → PostgreSQL
API exposes /metrics → Prometheus scrapes → Grafana visualizes

Features
- Secure user registration and login using JWT
- RESTful CRUD operations for library resources
- Prometheus metrics exposed at route /metrics
- Containerized multi-service environment (API, DB, Prometheus, Grafana)
- Real-time request monitoring via Grafana dashboards
